GOVERNMENT OF INDIA
CABINET SECRETARIAT
(Department of Cabinet Affairs)
IMMEDIATE
New Delhi, the 13th March, 1967.
The undersigned is directed to state that the Members
of the new Council of Ministers shown in the enclosed list
assumed office with effect from the forenoon of Monday,
March 13, 1967.
(D.P. Chopra)
for Cabinet Secretary.
To
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
Copy with a copy of the enclosure forwarded to the
Secretary to the Prime Minister/the Joint Secretary to the
Prime Minister/the Private Secretary to the Prime Minister,
for information.
Copy with a copy of the enclosure forwarded to the
Secretary to the Presldent/the Se retary to the Vice-
President, for information.
(D.P. Chopra)
Under Secretary to the Cabinet.
Copy with a copy of the enclosure forwarded to all
Secretaries/Special Secretaries/Additional Secretaries to the
Government of India/Chairman, Railway Board/Secretary,
Election Commission, for information.
Copy with a copy of the enclosure forwarded to all
Ministries of the Government of India/Lok Sabha Secretariat/
Rajya Sabha Secretariat, for information.
(D.P. Chopra)
Under Secretary to the Cabinet.
